languageName.langInfo: Urdu is the official language of North India, Pakistan, and Fiji. Pimsleur's Urdu teaches 'Hindustani,' and only focuses on the Urdu register/dialect of Hindustani. While Standard Urdu may be spoken in Pakistan, most Pakistanis and Indian Muslims speak Hindustani.  Learn Urdu today with Pimsleur.

languageName.langInfo: Albanian is spoken by about 6 million people, mainly in Albania and Kosovo. There are 2 principal dialects: Gheg, the northern dialect, and Tosk, the southern dialect and official language of the Republic of Albania. Pimsleur's Albanian teaches the Tosk dialect. Learn Albanian today with Pimsleur.
